item.title: Prayer bpn6454 in Sesotho
item.description: Oho Morena, Molimo oa ka! Thusa baratuoa ba Hau ho tiea Tumelong, ea Hau, ho tsamaea Tseleng ea Hau, ho tiea Tseleng ea Hau. Ba abele mosa oa Hau ho hlola liteko tsa nama le bobe, ho latela leseli la tataiso ea khalalelo ea Hau. Ke Uena Ea-Matla, Ea-Mosa, Ea-Iphilisang, Seabi, Ea-Kutloelo-Bohloko, E Moholo-holo, Ea Khauhelo Eohle (Source category: Thuso) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6454)
